      <para id="element-591">Each assignment is designated by a <emphasis>column</emphasis>, which is a vertical list of numbers. (This is easy to remember if you picture columns in Greek architecture, which are big and tall and…well, you know…vertical.)

</para><exercise id="id11045914"><problem id="idm4729360">
