<para id="element-73">Finally, it is possible to <emphasis>add</emphasis> or <emphasis>subtract </emphasis>matrices. But you can only do this when the matrices have the same dimensions!!! If two matrices do not have exactly the same dimensions, you cannot add or subtract them. If they do have the same dimensions, you add and subtract them just by adding or subtracting each individual cell.</para>

